Windows SDK (DWM / SetWindowCompositionAttribute)
  License: Microsoft Windows SDK License Agreement (proprietary)
  The DWM blur effect uses dwmapi.lib and the undocumented
  SetWindowCompositionAttribute API, both part of the Windows SDK.
  These are free to call from applications but are NOT MIT-licensed.
  Redistribution of Windows SDK binaries (dwmapi.dll etc.) is governed
  by Microsoft's terms — however dwmapi.dll ships with Windows itself
  and does not need to be redistributed.
  https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/downloads/windows-sdk/

